\"container-renseignements\">\n<div>Ouvert de 11:00 à 15:00 tous les jours sauf le lundi</div>\n<div><i class=\"fas fa-phone\"></i> 03 84 69 18 18</div>\n<div><a href=\"https://fr-fr.facebook.com/mandala.strasbourg/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><i class=\"fab fa-facebook-f\"></i></a> Facebook</div>\n<div><a href=\"mandala@gmail.com\"><i class=\"fas fa-envelope\"></i></a> Email</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<iframe class=\"imap\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2639.2693821597454!2d7.738202650961429!3d48.58554072773192!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x4796c84943418341%3A0xba4e2fd0a1736a7a!2sRestaurant+Mandala!5e0!3m2!1sfr!2sfr!4v1529479139567\" height=\"250\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;\" data-mce-type=\"bookmark\" class=\"mce_SELRES_start\">﻿</span><span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;\" data-mce-type=\"bookmark\" class=\"mce_SELRES_start\">﻿</span></iframe>', 'Restaurant Mandala à Strasbourg', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '217-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-11-05 13:05:55', '2019-11-05 12:05:55', '', 217, 'https://skergoat.com/wordpress/2019/11/05/217-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
